<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<title>NPK Deficiency Detected - iGreenMon</title>
	</head>

	<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 2rem; color: #333">
		<h2>NPK Deficiency Detected</h2>
		<p>Hi <%= user %>,</p>
		<p>
			Our system has detected a possible nutrient deficiency in your greenhouse
			<strong><%= greenhouse %></strong>.
		</p>
		<p>
			The detection was made using your camera 
			<strong><%= esp32Cam %></strong> during a capture:
		</p>
		<p style="margin: 1rem 0; color: #555">
			<strong>Capture File:</strong> <%= capture %><br />
			<strong>Detected Issue:</strong> <%= class %><br />
			<strong>Confidence:</strong> <%= (confidence * 100).toFixed(2) %>%
		</p>
		<p style="margin: 2rem 0; color: #555">
			Please sign in to your iGreenMon account to view the image and detailed
			analysis of this detection.
		</p>
		<p style="margin-top: 2rem">
			Stay healthy, <br />
			The iGreenMon Team
		</p>
	</body>
</html>
